reviewText: A must have course if you are trying to learn about Cloud computing and Software Defined Networking. The course provides very interactive environment through the quizzes and hands-on workshops. You will DEFINITELY not pass the quizzes on your first try. But it will encourage you to watch the videos again and then understand the topics more deeply. And so, you will do better in your next try.I took this course as I wanted to implement SDN using Ryu controller on my project work. After completing this course, I am confident that I can complete my work successfully.
Great course, but difficult quizzes for me.
Muy buen curso para entender como funcionan las redes en un centro de datos virtualizado. Y asi introducirse a las redes SDN dentro de esos entornos.
